## Expected Impact

| Improvement | Est. FPS Gain | Effort |
|---|---|---|
| ONNX inference | **+50–200%** | Low (one export script) |
| Frame skipping (process every 2nd) | **+80–100%** | Low |
| Resolution downscale (1080→640) | **+30–60%** | Low |
| Threaded capture | **+10–20%** | Medium |
| Shared `core.py` module | 0% (code quality) | Medium |
| **Combined** | **~3–5× faster** | — |

