## Verification Plan

### Automated
- Run `python export_onnx.py` → confirm `yolov8n.onnx` is generated
- Run `python track.py --source 0 --onnx yolov8n.onnx` → verify CLI tracking works
- Run `python main.py` → verify GUI tracking with FPS counter visible

### Manual
- Compare FPS before/after on the same video file
- Confirm tracking IDs remain stable across frames
- Test all GUI buttons (upload, camera, start/stop tracking, stop video)
